Bessie Barriscale https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bessie_Barriscale 0 Bessie Barriscale (September 30, 1884 – June 30, 1965) was an American silent-film and stage actress, and a major star for producer Thomas Ince in the late 1910s.
